description: Try our easy to follow Satay chicken subs recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
keywords: Chicken dishes,Quick & easy lunch,Dinner Made Easy,Chicken,Budget
name: Satay chicken subs Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 375g Australian RSPCA-approved satay style chicken kebabs
4 jumbo hot dog bread rolls, split

recipeInstructions.text: Preheat oven to 200°C/180°C fan-forced. Line 2 large baking trays with baking paper. Place skewers on 1 tray, the bake for 25 minutes or until cooked.
Place chips on remaining tray, then bake for the last 15 minutes of chicken cooking or until golden.
Meanwhile, prepare slaw kit according to packet instructions.
Remove chicken from skewers, then discard skewers. Fill rolls with slaw and chicken. Serve with chips.
